    v1 = wp.cos(((v1 + 0.87 - tmp + 0.24) - (v2 + 0.43 - v2 + 0.88)))
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.abs(wp.exp(v0 + 0.08)))
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.sin((v0 + 0.10 + v1 + 0.08)))
